{
  "stem": "26792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that was in the next town, next door almost-- of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for that time, you were not harassed, and you were--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, for instance, we couldn't go to that work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taken to the police station in Squallatile Street, Squalla Street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in a crowded room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Men, young, young-- everybody was young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Young men and women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we didn't know what they were going to do, because we had heard about the killings already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were sitting there without any bread and without any water all day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some girls were dragged away that didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still remember the name of one of those Latvians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, they took us to the old city-- in the future, I mean-- they took us to the old city of Riga, to clean up the mess.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the city had been partly destroyed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we, young and old, we were obliged to carry stones from one place to another, which didn't make sense, because we couldn't carry heavy stones.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They just wanted to make us work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, perhaps, I should mention that the guards were all Latvians, very young, from different Latvian nationalist organizations.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw a Jewish lady, a dentist, who was our neighbor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or I believe I never knew her-- knew her name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She collapsed because it was a very hot, July day, and I felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that young man, I don't remember the organization he belonged to, came up to me and said-- and this is what later happened now and again to me-- oh, you are not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're making fun.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's either your mother or father who is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
